      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-7">
            <h3 class="footer-title">Coding The Humanities</h3>
            <p>Coding the Humanities teaches scholars how to do research through coding.</p>
            </p>For more information, visit <a href="http://codingthehumanities.com/">codingthehumanities.com</a></p>
            </p>
            <ul class="list-inline banner-social-buttons">
              <li>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/codingthehumanities" target="_blank"> <span class="fui-facebook"></span></a>
              </li>
              <li>
